The Graphics Editor
[roman 10;pl;fj]


Entering the Graphics Editor

   There are two ways you can enter the Graphics Editor window: (1) by pulling the "Use Mini Editor" option and PICKing a graphic or (2) by pulling the "Create a Graphic" option. Both options are under the EDIT menu.


Description of the Graphics Editor Screen

   The Graphics Editor screen is composed of three main items: the menu bar, the status area, and the drawing board. Each of these items are shown below.


